<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:{$width}; margin-top: 1.2em;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/billiths-proposal/altruist.jpg" style="width:{$width};" alt="altruist.jpg" class="image" />
